import { firstValueReducer } from './firstValueReducer.js'
import { operationReducer } from './operationReducer.js'
import { secondValueReducer } from './secondValueReducer.js'
import { isFirstReducer } from './firstValueReducer.js'
import { combineReducers } from 'redux'

export const rootReducer = combineReducers({
    firstValue: firstValueReducer,
    operation: operationReducer,
    secondValue: secondValueReducer,
    isFirst: isFirstReducer
});
